arStrings.szText: Who the hell are you? No, don’t answer. You step lightly. (deep sniff) And you reek of dried blood. You're a killer. What do you want?
I heard you can teach me a few things.
Hmph. Let’s see if you’re worthy of teaching, first. I’ve got a job that needs doing. You help me, maybe I’ll help you.
I run with the Sisterhood of the Sightless Eye. One of ours is missing. Bakira.
She took two rookies and set out after an artifact. A coin. Help me find her. If you’re not all talk, you might learn a thing or two.
